---
title: Salmon, Smoked Haddock and Cod Pesto Penne with Spinach and Italian Style Cheese
description: Enjoy an elevated pescatarian version of classic pesto pasta with our Salmon, Smoked Haddock and Cod Pesto Penne. An easy creamy sauce ties it all together for a dish that's lightly indulgent.
